-----PLACEHOLDER-----
This file is replaced by the real ED25519 GPG public key during Cycle B
Phase 2 (T6 ops). Run the keypair generation command from ops/README.md
§1 then `gpg --armor --export backup@talib.local > ops/backup-public.asc`.

The nightly backup workflow imports this file and encrypts each pg_dump
to its recipient. The corresponding private key is NEVER committed —
it lives in 1Password + paper safe.

Until this file is replaced with the real key, .github/workflows/backup.yml
will fail at the "Import GPG public key" step.
